'''白林地菇'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|'''''Agaricus silvicola'''''}}），俗稱'''木蘑菇'''（{{lang|en|Wood Mushroom}}），是一種[[擔子菌門|擔子菌門]][[真菌|真菌]]，隸屬於[[伞菌属|伞菌属]]。這種真菌味道美味，呈白色，且廣泛地分佈於世界各地。

==分類==
白林地菇最早是由美國真菌學家{{link-en|卡羅·維塔迪尼|Carlo Vittadini}}於1832年描述的。當時，維塔迪尼以為這種真菌是[[四孢蘑菇|四孢蘑菇]]的變種，因此將之命名為'''四孢蘑菇白林變種'''。後來，[[查爾斯·霍頓·佩克|查爾斯·霍頓·佩克]]於1873年將其學名改為現名。<ref name="urlMycoBank: Agaricus silvicola">{{cite web|url=http://www.mycobank.org/BioloMICS.aspx?Table=Mycobank&Rec=768&Fields=All|title=''Agaricus silvicola'' (Vittad.) Peck|publisher=MycoBank. International Mycological Association|accessdate=November 11, 2012|archive-date=2013-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203003719/http://www.mycobank.org/BioloMICS.aspx?Table=Mycobank&Rec=768&Fields=All|dead-url=no}}</ref>其[[植物學名命名法|學名]]中的「''{{lang|la|silvicola}}''」源自[[拉丁文|拉丁文]]，意思是「白色樹林」。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.first-nature.com/fungi/agaricus-silvicola.php |title=Agaricus silvicola, Wood Mushroom - First Nature |access-date=2013-12-02 |archive-date=2017-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171224000429/http://www.first-nature.com/fungi/agaricus-silvicola.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 描述 ==
白林地菇的[[菌蓋|菌蓋]]直徑長5–10厘米（2.0–3.9英寸），呈凸面狀，呈淡奶油色，但在碰傷時會變成黃赭色。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.foragingguide.com/mushrooms/sp/wood_mushroom |title=Wood Mushroom - Agaricus silvicola |access-date=2013-12-02 |archive-date=2020-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200222181742/http://www.foragingguide.com/mushrooms/sp/wood_mushroom |dead-url=no }}</ref>其[[菌柄|菌柄]]高5–8厘米，厚1–1.5厘米，與菌蓋的顏色相同，且—有著一個脆弱的[[菌環|菌環]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mushroomexpert.com/agaricus_silvicola.html |title=Agaricus silvicola - MushroomExpert |access-date=2013-12-02 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126061422/http://www.mushroomexpert.com/agaricus_silvicola.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>其[[菌褶|菌褶]]起初呈淡粉灰色，隨着年齡增加會變成黑褐色。其子實層是自由下垂的。<ref>[http://wildaboutbritain.co.uk/wood-mushroom Wood Mushroom - Wild About Britain] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203232224/http://wildaboutbritain.co.uk/wood-mushroom |date=2013-12-03 }}</ref>其菌肉呈白色，在碰傷或切割後會變成黃赭色，並有著近似茴香的氣味。<ref name=Phillips06>{{cite book|author=Roger Phillips|year=2006|title =Mushrooms|publisher=Pan MacMillan|isbn=0-330-44237-6}}</ref>其[[孢子印|孢子印]]呈紫褐色。其[[擔孢子|擔孢子]]的大小為5–6 x 3–4微米。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rogersmushrooms.com/gallery/DisplayBlock~bid~5501~gid~~source~gallerydefault.asp |title=Rogers Mushrooms - Agaricus silvicola Mushroom |access-date=2013-12-02 |archive-date=2016-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161224091323/http://www.rogersmushrooms.com/gallery/DisplayBlock~bid~5501~gid~~source~gallerydefault.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===類似物種===
*[[野蘑菇|野蘑菇]]（{{lang|la|''Agaricus arvensis''}}），有着一個形狀類似齒輪的菌環，味道非常美味。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mushroomexpert.com/agaricus_arvensis.html |title=Mushroom Expert - ''Agaricus arvensis'' |access-date=2013-12-02 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227023335/http://www.mushroomexpert.com/agaricus_arvensis.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*[[四孢蘑菇|四孢蘑菇]]（{{lang|la|''Agaricus campestris''}}），通常比野蘑菇細小，菌褶在年輕時呈粉紅色，味道非常美味。<ref>{{cite book|last=Grigson|first=Jane |authorlink=|title=The Mushroom Feast|url=https://archive.org/details/mushroomfeast0000grig_s9u1|year=1975|publisher=Penguin |place=[[London|London]]|isbn=0-14-046273-2}}</ref>
*[[毒鵝膏|毒鵝膏]]（{{lang|la|''Amanita phalloides''}}），有著如同小裙的菌環，且是致命的。<ref name=mykoweb>{{cite web|url=http://www.mykoweb.com/CAF/species/Agaricus_silvicola.html|title=California Fungi—Agaricus silvicola|accessdate=January 18, 2008|archive-date=2012-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120921231335/http://www.mykoweb.com/CAF/species/Agaricus_silvicola.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==分佈及生境==
白林地菇廣泛地分佈於北美洲和歐洲<ref name=Arora2nd>{{cite book|author=Arora, David|year=1986|title=Mushrooms Demystified|url=https://archive.org/details/mushroomsdemysti00aror_0|publisher=Ten Speed Press|isbn=0-89815-169-4}}</ref>，並主要在[[落葉林|落葉林]]和[[針葉林|針葉林]]中出現。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wildfooduk.com/mushroom-guides/wood-mushroom-mushroom/ |title=Wood Mushroom, Agaricus silvicola - Wild Food UK |access-date=2013-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171018083814/http://www.wildfooduk.com/mushroom-guides/wood-mushroom-mushroom |archive-date=2017-10-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>這種真菌主要在秋季出現，並常以單獨或一小群的形式出現。<ref name=Phillips06/>

==可食性==
白林地菇是一種美味的蘑菇，並且在歐洲經常被用作食材。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtsn.tn.it/bresadola/gallery.asp?code=137&lang=eng|title=Agaricus sylvicola (Vittad.) Peck|accessdate=January 18, 2008|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606010226/http://www.mtsn.tn.it/bresadola/gallery.asp?code=137&lang=eng|archivedate=2011年6月6日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.grzyby.pl/gatunki/Agaricus_silvicola.htm|title=Agaricus silvicola (Vittad.) Peck (1887)|accessdate=January 18, 2008|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226015827/https://grzyby.pl/gatunki/Agaricus_silvicola.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>但是，這種真菌在北美洲卻可能引致過敏，儘管白林地菇的過敏案例非常罕見。<ref name=mykoweb/>

